<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>The current $_dateFormat (line 58 of Zend/Service/Twitter.php) value isn't correctly interprated by twitter.
It often leads to empty responses when there has to be new tweeds.</p>

<p>I would therefore strongly suggest to use the same format as twitter uses itself in the responses:</p>

<p>Mon Feb 16 13:44:39 +0000 2009</p>

<p>$_dateFormat = 'D M d H:i:s O Y';</p>

    </div>
