        <p class="metadata">Posted by Jon Whitcraft (sidhighwind) on 2009-02-16T06:12:47.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>The problem with your format is it's not a valid HTTP-formatted date as the since header is being sent across in the header <em>If-Modified-Since</em></p>

<p>I suggest changing it to: <em>D, d M Y H:i:s T</em> so it's a valid HTTP-formatted date.</p>

